      "index": "b2M",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1732667777,
      "version": 1617,
      "versionNonce": 115626721,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1740507256583,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- API Contract: Defines how the external world interacts with the Domain.\n- Controller: Adapts to the API contract to communicate with the Domain.\n- SPI Contract: Specifies how the Domain communicates with external systems\n(databases, message queues, third-party services).\n- Client: Adapts according to SPI contract inorder to interact with external systems.\n- Domain Independence: The Domain remains unaffected by changes in external\nsystems, ensuring the core business logic stays intact.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- API Contract: Defines how the external world interacts with the Domain.\n- Controller: Adapts to the API contract to communicate with the Domain.\n- SPI Contract: Specifies how the Domain communicates with external systems (databases, message queues, third-party services).\n- Client: Adapts according to SPI contract inorder to interact with external systems.\n- Domain Independence: The Domain remains unaffected by changes in external systems, ensuring the core business logic stays intact.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
